import React from 'react'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import { User, Lock, Settings, LogOut, ChevronRight, ArrowLeft } from 'lucide-react'; const Profile = ({ user, theme, onLogout }) => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const isDark = theme === 'dark'; const styles = { // 1. GLOBAL CONTAINER pageContainer: { backgroundColor: isDark ? '#0f172a' : '#f1f5f9', minHeight: '100vh', width: '100%', fontFamily: "'Inter', sans-serif", display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', alignItems: 'flex-start', paddingTop: '20px', paddingBottom: '40px' }, // 2. CONTENT WRAPPER contentWrapper: { width: '100%', maxWidth: '480px', padding: '0 20px', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: '16px' }, // 3. HEADER header: { display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', marginBottom: '10px', position: 'relative', justifyContent: 'center' }, backBtn: { position: 'absolute', left: 0, cursor: 'pointer', color: isDark ? '#fff' : '#1e293b', padding: '8px' }, headerTitle: { fontSize: '18px', fontWeight: '700', color: isDark ? '#fff' : '#1e293b' }, // 4. MAIN CARD mainCard: { backgroundColor: isDark ? '#1e293b' : '#fff', borderRadius: '24px', padding: '35px 20px', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', alignItems: 'center', boxShadow: '0 4px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.03)', marginBottom: '5px' }, avatarWrapper: { width: '100px', height: '100px', borderRadius: '50%', padding: '3px', background: 'linear-gradient(to bottom right, #5c5cfc, #a78bfa)', marginBottom: '15px' }, avatar: { width: '100%', height: '100%', borderRadius: '50%', objectFit: 'cover', border: '4px solid #fff', backgroundColor: '#f1f5f9' }, name: { fontSize: '22px', fontWeight: '800', color: isDark ? '#fff' : '#1e293b', marginBottom: '4px' }, email: { fontSize: '14px', color: isDark ? '#cbd5e1' : '#64748b', // FIXED: Lighter in dark mode marginBottom: '16px' }, badge: { backgroundColor: '#5c5cfc', color: '#fff', padding: '6px 24px', borderRadius: '20px', fontSize: '13px', fontWeight: '600', border: 'none' }, // 5. INFO CARD infoCard: { backgroundColor: isDark ? '#1e293b' : '#fff', borderRadius: '20px', padding: '24px', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: '15px', boxShadow: '0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.02)' }, infoRow: { display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', fontSize: '13px' }, // FIXED: Made label visible in dark mode label: { color: isDark ? '#94a3b8' : '#64748b', fontWeight: '500' }, value: { color: isDark ? '#fff' : '#1e293b', fontWeight: '700' }, // 6. MENU BUTTONS menuBtn: { backgroundColor: isDark ? '#1e293b' : '#fff', borderRadius: '20px', padding: '16px 20px', display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'space-between', cursor: 'pointer', border: 'none', width: '100%', boxShadow: '0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.02)', marginBottom: '0px' }, menuLeft: { display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: '15px' }, iconBox: (bg, color) => ({ width: '40px', height: '40px', borderRadius: '12px', backgroundColor: bg, color: color, display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }), // FIXED: Menu text color logic menuText: (isRed) => ({ fontSize: '15px', fontWeight: '600', color: isRed ? '#ef4444' : (isDark ? '#fff' : '#1e293b') }) }; return (
{/* Header */}
navigate(-1)}>
Profile
{/* Main Profile Card */}

{user.name}

{user.email}

{/* College Details Card */}
College Name {user.college}
Register Number {user.regNo}
{/* Menu Actions */}
); }; export default Profile;
